that through the diplomatic channels there have been initiatives 
he said other countries in the region were involved in these 
contacts but to the best of my knowledge there has been no 
response 
my government has made approaches through diplomatic channels 
to iran among other countries in the region to my knowledge there 
has been no response to these approaches yet 
