elected under a nasserera law that sets aside half the seats on 
the board of a public company for workers 
previous strikes and demonstrations at other staterun 
industries allegedly involved members of leftist political parties 
and communists 
strikes and demonstrations are banned under an emergency law in 
force since oct 7 1981 a day after moslem extremists 
