im definitely going to rule that way if the government makes 
a motion carter said in my view the partnership interest is 
totally forfeitable 
the judge then softened his remarks by saying he would review 
the matter when both sides submitted written arguments 
on monday the jury in us district court in manhattan 
convicted the defendants after a fiveweek trial of racketeering 
racketeering conspiracy conspiracy and numerous counts of mail and 
wire fraud 
the jurors returned to court to consider forfeiture because the 
federal antiracketeering law allows it 
the case marked the first time securities professionals were 
accused of racketeering under the controversial law aimed at 
combating mobsters and drug pushers the racketeer influenced and 
corrupt organizations law provides heavy fines and lengthy prison 
terms 
the trial received widespread attention because it grew 
indirectly out of the ivan boesky insidertrading scandal that 
rocked wall street three years ago 
