measures price movements on all outstanding treasury issues with 
maturities of a year or longer was down 449 to 120080 
moodys investment grade corporate bond index which measures 
total return on a portfolio of 80 corporate bonds with maturities 
of five years or longer fell 030 to 33530 
in the taxexempt market the bond buyer index of 40 actively 
traded municipal bonds fell 332 point the average yield to 
maturity because of rounding remained at 716 percent 
yields on threemonth treasury bills fell to 788 percent as the 
discount fell 2 basis points to 763 percent yields on sixmonth 
bills rose to 782 percent as the discount rose 2 basis points to 
743 percent yields on oneyear bills rose to 768 percent as the 
discount rose 1 basis point to 717 percent 
a basis point is onehundredth of a percentage point the yield 
is the annualized return on an investment in a treasury bill the 
discount is the percentage that bills are selling below the face 
value paid at maturity 
the federal funds rate the interest on overnight loans between 
banks traded at 8 percent unchanged from late wednesday 
